<img src='themes//images/pixel.gif' height='5' width='1' border='0' alt=''/><br/>
</td></tr><tr><td class="article-table"><B>Tallon Zek Dead!</B><br />
We actually killed this guy nearly a week ago now I think, I've just been slacking on the updates and haven't bothered posting about it yet. So you can all stop bugging me about it now. Really cool encounter, like Vallon this is very well designed. He sloooooowly draws back on his bow, takes aim... then *plink!* and someone else eats one of his nasty arrows.<br />
<br />
<DIV ALIGN="center"><IMG SRC="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/271102/tallonzek.jpg" WIDTH="348" HEIGHT="429" ALT="" BORDER="2"></DIV><br />
<br />
Knocked him over twice now, along with another two kills of Vallon.<br />
<br />
<DIV ALIGN="center"><IMG SRC="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/271102/tzcorpse.jpg" ALT="" WIDTH="600" HEIGHT="334" BORDER="0"><br />
<br />
<IMG SRC="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/271102/vzcorpse.jpg" ALT="" WIDTH="600" HEIGHT="291" BORDER="0"><br />
</DIV><br />
<br />
They also dropped us some pretty decent loots, some of the best we've found in PoP so far:<br />
<br />
<DIV ALIGN="center">Tallon:<br />
<A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Visor of Endless Sight&path=itempics&img=visorofendlesssight.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Visor of Endless Sight</A> - <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Veteran\'s Battle Charm&path=itempics&img=veteransbattlecharm.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Veteran's Battle Charm</A><br />
<br />
Vallon:<br />
<A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Furious Hammer of Zek&path=itempics&img=furioushammerofzek.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Furious Hammer of Zek</A> - <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Obsidian Scimitar of War&path=itempics&img=obsidianscimitarofwar.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Obsidian Scimitar of War</A><br />
<A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Girdle of the Tactician&path=itempics&img=girdleofthetactician.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Girdle of the Tactician</A> - <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Pendant of the Triumphant Victor&path=itempics&img=pendantofthetriumphantvictor.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Pendant of the Triumphant Victor</A><br />
</DIV><br />
<br />
We spent some time exploring in PoTactics, too, and came to one major conclusion: while painful, stampedes are just plain <I>cool</I>.<br />
<br />
<DIV ALIGN="center"><IMG SRC="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/271102/stampede.jpg" WIDTH="600" HEIGHT="195" ALT="" BORDER="0"></DIV><br />
<br />
<HR SIZE=1 WIDTH=50% ALIGN="center"><br />
<br />
<B>More random stuff</B><br />
<br />
We've also found the time to kill Behemoth twice, finish off 2 more HoH trials to gain access to HonorB (/wave Mr. Marr), tried Bertox ring a couple of times, and even managed to sneak in a depressingly easy trip back to VT for some of that lovely free loot. Some of the misc. PoP loots from all of that: <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Darwol\'s Cleaver&path=itempics&img=darwolscleaver.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Darwol's Cleaver</A>, <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Innovator\'s Hammer&path=itempics&img=innovatorshammer.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Innovator's Hammer</A>, <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Intricately Inscribed Band&path=itempics&img=intricatelyinscribedband.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Intricately Inscribed Band</A>, <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Platoon Leader\'s Pauldrons&path=platoonleaderspauldrons&img=imagename.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Platoon Leader's Pauldrons</A>, <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Warder\'s Ornate Broadsword&path=itempics&img=wardersornatebroadsword.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Warder's Ornate Broadsword</A>, <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Gem Bladed Axe&path=itempics&img=gembladedaxe.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Gem Bladed Axe</A>, <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Coil of Twisted Platinum Wire&path=itempics&img=coiloftwistedplatinumwire.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Coil of Twisted Platinum Wire</A>, <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Drape of Wings&path=itempics&img=drapeofwings.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Drape of Wings</A>.<br />
<br />
In a complete change of pace from most of the recent content, we paid a visit to Kael Drakkel again recently for a late night sojourn with our big orange buddy, the AoW. We had around 39 people there, with 5 clerics, and despite almost losing it near half way, we managed to hold on for a very fun victory. Loot was pretty nice for such a short after hours romp, too.. BoC, bow, pants and a mask from the Avatar, Statue dropped a BP, cloak, hammer, and a ST key, while Vindi was also kind enough to drop a BP. I think pretty much all the loots upgraded someone there, not bad for content two expansions old.<br />
<br />
<DIV ALIGN="center"><IMG SRC="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/271102/behemothtrain.jpg" ALT="" WIDTH="600" HEIGHT="162" BORDER="0"></DIV><br />
<br />
<DIV ALIGN="center"><IMG SRC="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/271102/bertring1.jpg" WIDTH="600" HEIGHT="231" ALT="" BORDER="0"></DIV><br />
<br />
<DIV ALIGN="center"><A HREF="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/271102/bertring2.jpg"><IMG SRC="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/271102/bertring2_tn.jpg" WIDTH="300" HEIGHT="195" ALT="" BORDER="0"></A><BR>(click to enlarge)</DIV><br />
<br />
<HR SIZE=1 WIDTH=50% ALIGN="center"><br />
<br />
<IMG SRC="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/271102/zarchspam.jpg" WIDTH="521" HEIGHT="28" ALT="" BORDER="0><br />
<br />
<IMG SRC="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/271102/bineman.jpg" WIDTH="266" HEIGHT="20" ALT="" BORDER="0"><br />
<br />
<IMG SRC="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/271102/faunconfused.jpg" WIDTH="509" HEIGHT="29" ALT="" BORDER="0"><br />
<br />
<IMG SRC="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/271102/gimickconfused.jpg" WIDTH="327" HEIGHT="20" ALT="" BORDER="0"><br />
<br />
<IMG SRC="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/271102/gimickreaver.jpg" WIDTH="434" HEIGHT="101" ALT="" BORDER="0"><br />
<br />
<IMG SRC="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/271102/poplytree.jpg" WIDTH="446" HEIGHT="18" ALT="" BORDER="0"><br /><br /></td></tr></table><br/>
