</td></tr><tr><td class="article-table"><table border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=2 align=center><tr><td align="left" valign="top"><br />
Nothing much new to report - we've been progressing slowly but steadily through the new expansion, with most of our recent focus having been on the crypt of decay and the events it contains. High Priest has died twice thus far, so with any luck we'll be able to spend some time throwing ourselves at the ring of bertox soon. If anyone from VI happens to read this page by chance, please do something about the encounter with the skeleton spawns. I'm sure you know which one I mean (it's pictured on the right there) - I have no problems dying to the actual adds during a fight, but dying because the adds caused so much video lag as to render the game unplayable gets pretty annoying.<br />
<br />
In other news, we killed Aerin again to get a bunch more people flagged for Halls of Honor, also got <A HREF="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/151102/behemoth.jpg">Behemoth</A> to around 50% before he decided to eat us and poof back on to the roof. Knocked over <A HREF="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/151102/terris.jpg">Terris</A> once more, and spent a fair bit of time running around Torment exploring the lower depths of one mob's <A HREF="http://members.iinet.net.au/~freeth/eqscreens/lcupdates/151102/intestine.jpg">intestinal tract</A> as well as some oh-so-fun key camping for Saryrn's tower. Finally, we wound up with a first shot at Ryda'Dar in HoH, who looks like he will prove a challenge in the near future (if the trigger doesn't get &quot;accidentally&quot; blown by curious wizards).<br />
<br />
Picked up a bunch of random loots from around the place, nothing earth shattering but linked here since I've been slacking on the loot posts recently.<br />
<br />
<B>Aerin`Dar</B>: <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Shoulderpads of the Visionary&path=itempics&img=shoulderpadsofthevisionary.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Shoulderpads of the Visionary</A> x2.<br />
<br />
<B>High Priest cycle</B>: <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Boneshod Greatstaff&path=itempics&img=boneshodgreatstaff.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Boneshod Greatstaff</A>, <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Diseased Skullcase&path=itempics&img=diseasedskullcase.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Diseased Skullcase</A>, <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Bone Carved Shortbow&path=itempics&img=bonecarvedshortbow.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Bone Carved Shortbow</A>, <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Spiked Skull Mace&path=itempics&img=spikedskullmace.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Spiked Skull Mace</A>, <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Stitched Flesh Neckalce&path=itempics&img=stitchedfleshnecklace.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Stitched Flesh Neckalce</A>[sic], <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Band of Flayed Flesh&path=itempics&img=bandofflayedflesh.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Band of Flayed Flesh</A>, <A HREF="#" onClick="window.open('http://www.lotuscult.com/~tase/updates/lootimg.php?itemname=Rotting Eye Mask&path=itempics&img=rottingeyemask.jpg','loot','height=280,width=470,resizable'); return false">Rotting Eye Mask</A>.<br />
